# MMS-MFC Test Framework Installation Plan

## Executive Summary

This plan details the installation and configuration of a comprehensive test framework for the MMS-MFC monorepo, covering:

1. **Playwright** - E2E testing for the Next.js 14 frontend (7 pages)
2. **Vitest** - Unit/integration testing for both frontend (React/Blueprint.js) and backend (Fastify)
3. **pytest** - Unit testing for the Python OR-Tools solver

---

## 1. Directory Structure

The recommended test structure follows monorepo best practices with tests co-located with code:

```
MFC/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/
│   │   ├── __tests__/                    # Unit tests (Vitest)
│   │   │   ├── components/
│   │   │   │   ├── dashboard/
│   │   │   │   │   └── KPICard.test.tsx
